Feature                Headers                                    Properties
Location               Inside the Message object                  Inside the Exchange object
External Visibility    Yes (Sent to Kafka, HTTP, JMS, etc.)       No (Stays inside your Java app)
Lifecycle              Can be lost if a new Message is created    Persists until the Exchange is finished
Standard Usage         Protocol metadata (URL, Filename)          Route state/logic (Flags, Retry counts)
DSL Syntax              ".setHeader(""key"", value)"              ".setProperty(""key"", value)"
Simple Expression      ${header.key}                              ${exchangeProperty.key}
